Azure pricing and subscription
=============================

Managing prices for any cloud services is major and imp task.
All the resources are associated with a subscription and subscription is directly tied with the account holder identity. There can be multiple subscriptions in an account and thats
the best way to manage subscription for each department.
Finance will have their own subscription, Sales team will have their, Admin team, Dev team etc....
Its easy to manage budgets and pay the amount when invoice generates by Microsoft Azure.

- A billing cycle on Azure is 30 or 60 days.

Management group
================
- Its used to manage when you have multiple subscriptions. YOu can manage access , policies and compliance in bulk.
Cost Management
==============
Azure cost mgmt will be available on portal to check costs.
